<h2>Introduction</h2>
<p>Some time in the middle of 2017, Ruby (my girlfriend) and I decided it was time to take a trip to explore the southern part of Mexico, our North American neighbor. The trip took place from February 21 to March 4, 2018 and spanned multiple cities in the Mexican states of Chiapas and Quintana Roo. Our three main stops were San Cristobal de las Casas (Chiapas), Palenque (Chiapas), and the coastal city of Tulum (Quintana Roo).</p>

